From 13bcc9502c0343232f5fda64524b9fe1d2c04320 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Sun, 26 Apr 2026 15:06:10 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add debug logging mode for tool call troubleshooting

- Add DEBUG env variable support (DEBUG=1 or DEBUG=true to enable)
- Add src/utils/log.js: structured logger with debug/info/warn/error levels
- Add logging to openai-bridge: model selection, prompt injection, tool call parsing results
- Add logging to deepseek-proxy: upstream requests, token refresh, PoW challenge
- Add logging to openai-tool-parser: XML match results, parse failure details
- Add logging to openai-routes: request entry, auth, error handling
- Update .env.example with DEBUG option

When DEBUG is off (default), only info/warn/error are shown.
When DEBUG is on, full request flow is traced for diagnosing tool call failures.
---
 .env.example                       |  1 +
 src/config.js                      |  4 ++++
 src/routes/openai-routes.js        |  9 +++++++++
 src/services/deepseek-proxy.js     | 12 ++++++++++++
 src/services/openai-bridge.js      | 17 +++++++++++++++++
 src/services/openai-tool-parser.js | 12 ++++++++++--
 src/utils/log.js                   | 24 ++++++++++++++++++++++++
 7 files changed, 77 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 src/utils/log.js

